==English==
===Etymology===
[[Back-formation]] from '''Mafeking''' ([[w:Mafikeng|Mafikeng]]) [[punningly]] treated as a [[present participle]], from the celebrations in London after the relief of Mafeking during the [[w:Boer War|Boer War]].

